name: Scooting Squirrel Limited Edition Screen print
description:
Scooting Squirrel is an original limited edition silk screen print from the amazing 'Animal Alphabet' collection. These quirky, graphic characters are designed & printed by Kay Vincent in a studio in south east London. 

" When screen printing my designs I like to drift off into the world of the character & imagine what they are up to! 'Scooting' around is a popular mode of transport for the little people of my local hood in East Dulwich, which inspired my letter 'S'. This Scooting Squirrel is going super fast, so fast that I think his yellow pom pom hat is about to fly off, which is not good as he uses it to store his nuts!" 

Inspiration comes from Kay's treasured collection of 50's and 60's children's storybooks and vintage picture flash cards, which she finds on her regular rummaging trips to vintage markets & junk shops, the nostalgic charm of which has been clearly captured in these visual delights which appeal to adults and children alike - perfect for a nursery.

Limited Edition of 100, signed & numbered
Printed on 300gsm Somerset Soft White Satin paper.
Paper size 28.5 x 38cm
Frame not included but print cleverly fits in off the shelf frames

description:
